TEXT.S: Devin Booker unu syubay kanas-malimiunduay nu Amilika NBA nisakaput, u mikilac zikuzay mimaliay. Devin Booker i 2015 a mihcaan NBA sapapili' mimaliay a kawaw, saka 1 ku uwac atu silsil 13, namapili' tu nu Phoenix Suns putiput. 10 a bulad 30 a demiad, 1996 a mihcaan, Devin Booker u kawaw niza sa u miunduay.
